Class JobListEntryRecord

java.lang.Object
uk.ac.manchester.spinnaker.alloc.model.JobListEntryRecord
public class JobListEntryRecord extends Object
Entry in a table of machines. The table is like this:

6037654 ready on 1 SpiNNaker1M 11/07/2021 13:04:43 60.0 NMPI (10.11.192.12)
